{"tid":2324860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳招港澳籍公務員446人爭5職位   244人爭1街道辦職位","createTime":"2020-12-14T08:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T08:54:07.000Z","uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2ace929b79bf6614e1300413e25b9418798cad63","tid":2324860,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T08:44:20.000Z","msg":"2020年度深圳市公務員考試於12日、13日舉行，共有5個職位定向港澳選拔，這是深圳公務員考試首次有港澳籍人士參加。<br />\n據中新社13日報道，這次考試共吸引了446名港澳籍人士報名。離香港較近的福田區福保街道辦事處的一個職位吸引了244人報考，成為最熱門職位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/561434/%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E9%A6%96%E6%8B%9B%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E7%B1%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E5%85%B1446%E4%BA%BA%E7%88%AD5%E8%81%B7%E4%BD%8D-244%E4%BA%BA%E7%88%AD%E7%A6%8F%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%A1%97%E9%81%93%E8%BE%A6%E8%81%B7%E4%BD%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F561434%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%259C%25B3%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%258B%259B%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E7%25B1%258D%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2585%25B1446%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2588%25AD5%25E8%2581%25B7%25E4%25BD%258D-244%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2588%25AD%25E7%25A6%258F%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25A1%2597%25E9%2581%2593%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E8%2581%25B7%25E4%25BD%258D&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725PZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=ffad4949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/561434/%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E9%A6%96%E6%8B%9B%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E7%B1%8D%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E5%85%B1446%E4%BA%BA%E7%88%AD5%E8%81%B7%E4%BD%8D-244%E4%BA%BA%E7%88%AD%E7%A6%8F%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%A1%97%E9%81%93%E8%BE%A6%E8%81%B7%E4%BD%8D</a>"},{"pid":"3650a8a48db277c36e2301dd5440184dc91ca482","tid":2324860,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T08:54:07.000Z","msg":"嘩，一做官就發發啦！"}]}